Written evidence submitted by Promega UK Ltd (FSS042)[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Does the Government have an effective strategy for forensic science in the UK and is it sufficient to support forensic science R&amp;D and criminal justice?
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
