[normal]NOTE: This list is not intended to be definitive and other chemistries may also be in use in these countries
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]France 
[normal]is
[normal] currently using 
[normal]PowerPlex 
[normal]18D for database samples and 
[normal]PowerPlex 
[normal]21 for casework.  Spain will be implementing
[normal] PowerPlex
[normal] Fusion in the near future for casework and database samples. Belgium is already using 
[normal]European 
[normal]NGC 
[normal]STR
[normal] systems and are considering moving to a global kit
[normal] (such as PowerPlex Fusion or GlobaFiler)
[normal] in the near future. 
